Ing '''WorldCat''' metung yang [[:en:union catalog|union catalog]] a mag-grupu-grupu o maglarawan dikil kareng dake kareng coleccion o pamitipun da reng 71,000 a [[library|aklatan]] kareng 112 a bangsa<ref name="statistics">{{Cite web
| url         =http://www.oclc.org/ca/en/worldcat/statistics/default.htm
| title       =WorldCat facts and statistics
| year        =2009
| publisher   =[[Online Computer Library Center]]
| accessdate  =November 4, 2009
}}</ref> a kayabe king [[Online Computer Library Center]] (OCLC) a cooperativang pangyatu. Tinikdo re at mamantinian deng kayanib a aklatan. 

Melalang ya kanitang 1971, at atin yang maigit 150 milion a miayaliwang simpan (''records'') a tuturu kareng 1.4 bilion a banding pisical ampong digital kareng maigit 470 amanu.<ref name="statistics"/> Ya ing pekamaragul a [[bibliographic]] database king yatu. Ing OCLC darake neng alang bayad ing WorldCat kareng aklatan, dapat ing catalogo batayan de reng aliwang serviciong OCLC a maki bayad (anti king resource sharing ampong collection management). Ing WorldCat tetag neng [[Fred Kilgour]] kanitang l967.<ref>Margalit Fox, [http://www.nytimes.com/2006/08/02/us/02kilgour.html "Frederick G. Kilgour, Innovative Librarian, Dies at 92"] (obituary), ''New York Times'', August 2, 2006.</ref>

